{
  "id": "government-application",
  "name": "Full Government Application Form",
  "category": "complex",
  "summary": "Complete multi-page government application with conditional fields, file uploads, common fields, FOIP notice, and declaration checkbox",
  "whenToUse": [
    "Complex government service applications (permits, licenses, benefits)",
    "Reference for how to combine multiple form features into a cohesive application"
  ],
  "dataSchema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "applicantName": {
        "$ref": "https://adsp.alberta.ca/common.v1.schema.json#/definitions/personFullName"
      },
      "email": { "type": "string", "format": "email", "minLength": 1 },
      "phone": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 },
      "mailingAddress": {
        "$ref": "https://adsp.alberta.ca/common.v1.schema.json#/definitions/postalAddressAlberta"
      },
      "applicationType": {
        "type": "string",
        "enum": ["New Application", "Renewal", "Amendment"]
      },
      "hasSupplementaryDocs": { "type": "boolean" },
      "supplementaryDocument": { "type": "string", "format": "file-urn" },
      "additionalNotes": { "type": "string" },
      "iDeclare": {
        "type": "boolean",
        "allOf": [{ "enum": [true] }]
      }
    },
    "required": ["email", "phone", "applicationType", "iDeclare"],
    "if": {
      "properties": {
        "hasSupplementaryDocs": { "const": true }
      }
    },
    "then": {
      "required": ["supplementaryDocument"]
    }
  },
  "uiSchema": {
    "type": "Categorization",
    "options": {
      "variant": "pages",
      "title": "Government Service Application",
      "subtitle": "Apply for the program"
    },
    "elements": [
      {
        "type": "Category",
        "label": "Personal Information",
        "options": { "sectionTitle": "About You" },
        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "HelpContent",
            "options": {
              "markdown": true,
              "help": ["Please provide your contact information. All fields marked with * are required."]
            }
          },
          { "type": "Control", "scope": "#/properties/applicantName" },
          {
            "type": "HorizontalLayout",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "Control",
                "scope": "#/properties/email",
                "options": { "help": "We'll use this to send you updates on your application." }
              },
              {
                "type": "Control",
                "scope": "#/properties/phone",
                "options": { "help": "Include area code (e.g., 780-555-0123)." }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "Category",
        "label": "Mailing Address",
        "options": { "sectionTitle": "About You" },
        "elements": [{ "type": "Control", "scope": "#/properties/mailingAddress" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "Category",
        "label": "Application Details",
        "options": { "sectionTitle": "Your Application" },
        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "Control",
            "scope": "#/properties/applicationType",
            "options": { "format": "radio" }
          },
          {
            "type": "Control",
            "scope": "#/properties/hasSupplementaryDocs",
            "label": "Do you have supplementary documents to upload?"
          },
          {
            "type": "Control",
            "scope": "#/properties/supplementaryDocument",
            "options": { "variant": "dragdrop" },
            "rule": {
              "effect": "SHOW",
              "condition": {
                "scope": "#/properties/hasSupplementaryDocs",
                "schema": { "const": true }
              }
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "Control",
            "scope": "#/properties/additionalNotes",
            "options": {
              "multi": true,
              "help": "Provide any additional information relevant to your application."
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "Category",
        "label": "Review & Submit",
        "options": { "sectionTitle": "Submission" },
        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "HelpContent",
            "options": {
              "markdown": true,
              "help": [
                "#### Notice of Collection",
                "The personal information on this form is collected under the authority of Section 33(c) of the *Freedom of Information and Protection of Privacy Act* (FOIP). If you have any questions contact us at [support@gov.ab.ca](mailto:support@gov.ab.ca)."
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "Control",
            "scope": "#/properties/iDeclare",
            "options": {
              "text": "I declare that the information I have provided is true and correct to the best of my knowledge."
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  "notes": [
    "This combines: multi-page stepper, common fields ($ref), conditional file upload, FOIP notice, and declaration",
    "Section titles group related categories (pages) on the task list",
    "The if/then conditional makes supplementaryDocument required only when hasSupplementaryDocs is true",
    "Always pair SHOW/HIDE rules with matching if/then conditional validation in the data schema",
    "Use schemaDefinitionTool to load common schema definitions before using $ref for fullName and address",
    "The FOIP notice and declaration checkbox are required on most Alberta government forms"
  ]
}
